ISDA regularly hosts luncheons focusing on various risk management topics.
We would like to invite you to attend the next luncheon this Wednesday, May
9, 2001.  Please contact Scott Marra at the phone # listed below if you are
interested in attending.  Many thanks!  -- Stacy

